      {An obsolete old landline telephone. It has laid abandoned for many years, causing the white shell to somewhat yellow.
Investigation revealed that a large number of parts were missing, and the internal wiring had been ripped apart.}
      ]

      [
      {Whenever someone passes nearby, a hollow ringing sound will come from the phone.
Investigation into the origins of the phone have not produced results on its origins. Some speculate that it operates on magic.
Place the receiver to your ear, and you will hear voices from another world.}
      ]

      [
      {What happens after we die? I couldn't stop thinking about it, after I heard about my coworker's suicide.
It took a few days for people to find his body, but oddly enough, his face was still identifiable.
I still remember his smiling expression. I wonder if he saw a glimpse of what happens after death.
I wonder if it was beautiful.}
